caller_intent: Nathan Bell wanted to confirm receipt of a proposal email sent for carrier renewal confirmation and requested a resend since he hadn't received it.
resolution_steps: Glory Delancey Shine confirmed the proposal was sent to Nathan's email address (nbel@gbngi.com).
Nathan verified he hadn't received it and checked spam folders.
Glory offered to resend the proposal.
Glory resent the proposal and asked Nathan to confirm receipt.
knowledge_required: Proposal submission workflows for carrier renewals
Client communication protocols for document follow-ups
summary: Nathan Bell reported not receiving a critical proposal email for carrier renewal. Glory Delancey Shine confirmed the original send and resent the document. Nathan agreed to review the new email and provide confirmation once received.
